channel.title: To all msn messenger users
channel.description:
Ok there is a virus going around and it is sent to you by your friends, your friends did not send them it is a virus they got and it will look something like this
this was me and aj talking and he has it on his computer, do not accept this file, simply ignore it.

http://www.hftonline.com/forum/showthread.php?t=7671
if your smart enough you can get rid of it.
NOTE: i have no idea who did this and the picture i put on there is me and aj talking and thats what it might look like if you get it.
